import { OutlinedInput, Select } from "@mui/material"
import { InputWithValidate } from "./InputWithValidate"

export const InputCarDetailes = () => {



    /*
    { 
        id: 1,
        licensePlate: "36-375-97",
        carModelId: 1,
        numberOfSeats: 5,
        img: "Toyota_Corolla-Space.png",
        yearBook: 2017,
        automaticGear: true,
        driveTypeId: 2,
        pricePerHour: 30,
        fuelConsumptionPerKm: 12,
        balance: 30,
        city: "ירושלים",
        street: "שטראוס 25",
        available: false },
    */

    let licensePlateConditions = [
        { func: (value) => !(/^\d{7,8}$/.test(value) || value == ""), messege: "מספר רישוי לא תקין" }
    ]

    return <>

        <InputWithValidate conditions={licensePlateConditions} required label="מספר רישוי"></InputWithValidate>
        <Select
            value={"בחר מודל רכב"}
            label="Age"
            onChange={handleChange}
        >
            <MenuItem value={10}>Ten</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value={20}>Twenty</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value={30}>Thirty</MenuItem>
        </Select>



    </>

}
